take the keys from the table
move out of the circle and towards the television, then stop, and face the same round grey table
Put the keys in the empty box on the table
Take the box with the keys
cross the room to the couch in front of you
place the box on the right-side cushion of the couch.
tasks.task_desc: Place a box with keys in it on the couch

high_descs: Move to the coffee table nearest to two arm chairs.
Pick up the keys from the coffee table.
Move around to the left side of the coffee table.
Place the keys inside the box on the table.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Move around to the couch on the other side of the coffee table.
Place the box on the couch.
tasks.task_desc: Put the box on the coffee table on the couch with keys inside.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the long cabinet then turn right and walk past the circular stand on your right then turn right and walk to the couch.
Pick up the set of car keys on the couch.
Turn around and take a couple steps until you're even with the table on the left with a remote on it then turn left to face it.
Put the keys in the box.
Pick up the box with the keys in it.
Stand slightly to the right of where you got the keys.
Put the box on the couch near it's right arm.
tasks.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on the couch.

high_descs: Go around the coffee table and go to the couch.
Pick up the keys on the couch.
Turn to the coffee table.
Put the keys in the box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box with the keys in it.
Turn back to the sofa and go to the right side.
Set the box on the right side of the sofa.
tasks.task_desc: Set a box with keys inside on the sofa.

high_descs: Turn right and walk past the coffee table to stand in front of the leftmost cushion of the sofa.
Pick up the keys from the sofa.
Turn around and carry the keys to the coffee table, so you're facing the table and the sofa is to your left.
Place the keys in the open box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box with the keys in it from the table.
Carry the box to stand facing the center point of the sofa.
Place the box on the right cushion of the sofa.
tasks.task_desc: Place a box with keys inside on the sofa.
